      "ja": "週末はどうだった？",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, did you want with that the same guy?",
      "zh": "哦，你是跟同一個男生約會嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、その同じ男と会ったの？",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
