      "ja": "わかるでしょ。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, but you have to promise me at least one night this week you will take a night off from even thinking about coffee.",
      "zh": "是啊，但你得答應我這週至少有一晚不想咖啡。",
